<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Francesco Testa</author>
<hymn_number>3358</hymn_number>
<title>Change me</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 You are at work
 You're gonna do something new in me
 Though I don't know
 Lord I have no due what it is
 So I will let all
 My troubles and cares at your feet
 Spirit of God hear my call

[V2]
 Spirit of God
 Do your work in me
 Spirit of the Lord
 I call your name
 Remind me the works
 Of my Savior Christ
 You have the power to change me

[V3]
 I'll give you peace
 A peace this world knows nothing about
 You've never know
 Such a blessing before
 It's in My name
 Your stronghold and your refuge am I
 I'll never ever forsake you

[V4]
 So ask in My name
 My good will you will see in your life
 And I am with you always

[V5]
 Spirit of God
 Do your work in me
 Spirit of the Lord
 I call your name
 Remind me the words
 Of my Savior Christ
 You have the power to change me
 Lord change me</lyrics>
</song>